Custom Liquid Section

Yup, you read that write! This entire section is written right inside of the theme customizer. What's even cooler, is that the list below is made up of entries within the Saalt Wear Styles metaobject — none of that is actually written in this section!

Plus! All of the styling for this section is written in the theme customizer as well. The style tag is even using css variables from the theme.liquid file for the section's colors.🤯

{% liquid assign styles = '' for entry in shop.metaobjects.saalt_wear_styles.values assign styles = styles | append: entry.style_name unless forloop.last assign styles = styles | append: ', ' endunless endfor assign split_styles = styles | split: ', ' %}
